Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然我已经活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我的牺牲能拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不害怕 我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这家伙太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们快去找友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我来挡住它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你一个人挡住？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还有满开在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得向友奈道歉 带她一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东西无双 三好夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敬请看好我此生最大的疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树 这里能交给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 姐姐去找友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我去把友奈带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可别出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风学姐 上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就去友奈那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会开到最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}防护罩被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}园子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以一个人冲太前面哦 小鱼干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起保护好 友奈要回来的这片家园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡 看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那边是神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没完没了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全员弃舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神树大人在阻止我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我这次也不会退让
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路被…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡 做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么我来给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开路！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能靠精灵之力回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们回去吧 我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你宁可这么做 也不肯把她交给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 我这就救你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是如果我不牺牲 世界就会灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然必须有人牺牲 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不需要你…不需要任何人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想再有好朋友被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:10:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只要忍耐就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说真心话吧 害怕就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们既然是朋友 就向我求救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能说 但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想跟大家分开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们一直很拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么还要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好想 好想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}永远和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么会…为什么非要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我感谢神树大人 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果要得到新世界就得牺牲别人 牺牲朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要这种新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每个人都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你真的想拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再相信一次人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会继续过人类的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 对不起 都是我说太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我才要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对你做了好过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么办 世界要毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果世界真的要毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们也无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要紧的 好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们会作为人类去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者不屈 在哪里跌倒就在哪里站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了友奈的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有志者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社 Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者就靠毅力！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者之拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和以前不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牛鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}散花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是平时的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了友奈 身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烙印消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欢迎回来 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}于内陆山区至市区一带发生的大规模火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受灾面积一周内扩大至约一万公顷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.53,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由于长期避难 居民们倍感疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.30,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要求大赦针对接下来的事 拿出合理方针
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说 大赦早知道墙外的情况了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:16.01,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请看 本土已经化为了毫无生气的废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人们今后只能靠着有限的资源生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:20.27,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}涌出的石油据说是神树大人的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}孩子们是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}地之神消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失去庇护的人类 只能靠有限的资源活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定会发生混乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我为她们的选择感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新时代应当是孩子们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大人要为孩子负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是我们的天命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社变回了勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风学姐考上了高中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下一任社长竟然是树
